          "description": "This hospital did not meet my expectations because it is too expensive and when I requested an MRI for my autistic son, they did not know how to answer me or give me options. What they tell you is that if you want to do more tests, they will not help you with your concerns about autism. The worst thing of all is that they are not clear from the beginning. They also do not let you pay a small amount of money and they send you a form knowing that I do not apply for anything. Because in this state they only look at what your partner earns without seeing that the other party does not work and has expenses everywhere. Really, health care should not be so expensive for those of us who pay taxes and have children with conditions.",
