          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX61-qE1YtmvMGY_63vAPwM99E_m-vbUAqQhRWyjIXWF0ebMMKW=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100",
          "description": "Best hospital in NYC!!! The level of care was amazing. My wife had a procedure done and the attention shown to her was top notch. The doctors are some of the best in the country. The nurses and staff show a genuine sense of care. We felt very comfortable and confident during our time there. The bed side care is unmatched in NYC. The oncology department and the GYNECOLOGY department are the best in NYC hands down. Our insurance was excepted and we didn\u2019t come out o pocket. The billing department will work with your needs. I know countless people who have said they will not go to any other hospital. Every visit we were made to feel like we were the most important patient there. The doctors and nurses spent a lot of time explaining what they were going to do and what they thought would be our best options. Every question we asked was answered. I would highly recommend to anyone looking for the highest care available. Thank you!!!",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURZcVpLQTV3RRAB!2m1!1s0x0:0xbc2b81ee691a6c51!3m1!1s2@1:CIHM0ogKEICAgIDYqZKA5wE%7C%7C?hl=en",
